comments: Mobley (CLE) is in the lane for less than three seconds when he receives the pass and starts his upward shooting motion.
Turner (IND) initiates contact with Mobley's (CLE) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Mitchell (CLE) and Hield (IND) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Turner (IND) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Turner (IND) and Allen (CLE) mutually engage during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Hield (IND) reaches in and incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Mitchell (CLE) at the end of his drive.
Nesmith (IND) initiates contact with Mitchell's (CLE) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Mobley (CLE) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Mathurin (IND) and is not in a legal guarding position as contact occurs during Mathurin's (IND) upward shooting motion.
Turner (IND) initiates contact with Allen's (CLE) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
LeVert (CLE) reaches in and avoids making contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm during his drive.
Nembhard (IND) and Garland (CLE) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Allen (CLE) and Hield (IND) mutually engage as they come together during their pursuit of the loose ball.
Correctly called 24 second violation on CLE.
